Sentencas: In this study, lanthanum strontium cobalt ferrite cathodes surface-treated with lanthanum strontium cobaltite nanoparticles are synthesized using inkjet printing and their performances are evaluated using intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Lanthanum strontium cobaltite-infiltrated lanthanum strontium cobalt ferrite cathodes fabricated by inkjet printing for high-performance solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The porous lanthanum strontium cobalt ferrite cathode of an anode-support solid oxide fuel cell is prepared under optimized inkjet printing conditions.
Titulo: Lanthanum strontium cobaltite-infiltrated lanthanum strontium cobalt ferrite cathodes fabricated by inkjet printing for high-performance solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The surface treatment is performed by infiltrating a lanthanum strontium cobaltite ink followed by calcination.
Titulo: Lanthanum strontium cobaltite-infiltrated lanthanum strontium cobalt ferrite cathodes fabricated by inkjet printing for high-performance solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The lanthanum strontium cobalt ferrite cathode is evenly surface-covered with lanthanum strontium cobaltite nanoparticles, confirming the effectiveness of the inkjet printing for the cathode surface modification.
Titulo: Lanthanum strontium cobaltite-infiltrated lanthanum strontium cobalt ferrite cathodes fabricated by inkjet printing for high-performance solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The fuel cell performances are evaluated in the intermediate temperature range of 550-650 degrees C.
Titulo: Lanthanum strontium cobaltite-infiltrated lanthanum strontium cobalt ferrite cathodes fabricated by inkjet printing for high-performance solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The power is significantly improved even with a small addition of the surface lanthanum strontium cobaltite; the enhancement factor reaches the value of five.
Titulo: Lanthanum strontium cobaltite-infiltrated lanthanum strontium cobalt ferrite cathodes fabricated by inkjet printing for high-performance solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: An electrochemical impedance analysis confirms that the enhanced fuel cell performance is attributed to the reduced polarization impedance, significantly activating the surface catalysis.
Titulo: Lanthanum strontium cobaltite-infiltrated lanthanum strontium cobalt ferrite cathodes fabricated by inkjet printing for high-performance solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The addition of lanthanum strontium cobaltite retained the stability of the lanthanum strontium cobalt ferrite cell.
Titulo: Lanthanum strontium cobaltite-infiltrated lanthanum strontium cobalt ferrite cathodes fabricated by inkjet printing for high-performance solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: However, an excessive amount of lanthanum strontium cobaltite significantly reduces the cell performance.
Titulo: Lanthanum strontium cobaltite-infiltrated lanthanum strontium cobalt ferrite cathodes fabricated by inkjet printing for high-performance solid oxide fuel cells
